Design for generating Invoice

Method: POST, URL: /generateInvoice
Content-type: Application/json
Request: invValue, gstNo, status, note, description
Response: invId,message

Design for getting invoice by status
Method: GET URL: /getInvoiceByStatus/{status}
Request: status
Response: All invoices

Design for getting invoice by status and filtering the invoice value
Method: GET URL: /getInvoiceByFilter/{status}/{invValue}
Request: status,invValue
Response: All invoices


Design for get invoice by value

Method: GET, URL: /getInvoiceByValue/{invValue}
Request: invValue
Response: All invoices